{"tid":462784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉黃大仙5宗縱火　兩中一生被捕","createTime":"2017-11-09T01:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T14:20:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"cd878628e2c0f6b0ea53ed00afd58184c3304a09","tid":462784,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171109/20208875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F20208875&d=iI%2B77h8RqrB2XqvfLFJKPAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e300020b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F20208875&h=70285592\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171109/20208875</a><br />\n<br />\n涉黃大仙5宗縱火　兩中一生被捕<br />\n<br />\n港聞  <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黃大仙區7日內先後發生5宗縱火案，警方將案件交由黃大仙警區重案組第一隊合併調查後，於前日及昨日早上在黃大仙區內拘捕兩名中一男生，相信他們與本月3日鳳德道一條有露宿者棲身的行人隧道縱火案有關，正調查他們是否涉及其他縱火案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171109/large/09la7p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F09la7p12.jpg&h=2d8fb210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方拘捕兩名男生，疑與本月初黃大仙區內行人隧道縱火案有關。<br />\n<br />\n疑貪玩犯案　最高可囚終身<br />\n<br />\n涉縱火被捕兩名13歲男童為同學，家住黃大仙區，就讀九龍區一間中學一年級，同在寓所被捕，警方正調查他們犯案動機，不排除有人一時貪玩犯案。<br />\n<br />\n該5宗縱火案的首兩宗發生在本月1日及3日傍晚，鳳德道11號對開通往黃大仙祠的一條行人隧道先後發生縱火案，棲身在隧道內露宿者的家當及雜物被燒焚，幸無人受傷；另外在本周一凌晨，停泊在環鳳街後巷及黃大仙祠對開的3輛電單車遭人縱火燒毀；至前日凌晨，竹園北邨蕙園樓對開的電單車位又有3輛電單車被人縱火燒毀。<br />\n警方調查後懷疑連串縱火案有關連，交黃大仙警區重案組跟進。警方經追查後鎖定兩名涉案男學生，並於前晚及昨晨分別到兩人的住處將他們拘捕，而有人在警誡下已承認與行人隧道縱火案有關。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙警區刑事總督察王爾威強調，縱火是嚴重罪行，最高可被判終身監禁，呼籲市民若目擊案件，致電3661 6156與調查人員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃江奇"},{"pid":"f6b1056f410ee09c2526e37b741adf25948dce02","tid":462784,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28773b5b0bf4cc7a8bdc3c159ae78be418816170","tid":462784,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"衰過5毛"},{"pid":"b11b9371d9e7b6da2dbc3d3c021f65e925d16492","tid":462784,"uid":86051,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"縱火咁撚癲<br />\n好似好大獲"},{"pid":"7bd018d9fac138a54dd5253773f0c7debdbc6782","tid":462784,"uid":19552,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>縱火咁撚癲<br />\n好似好大獲</blockquote><br />\n家長：細路仔係咁架啦 咁大個人咪同細路仔計較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccef05d7ddcea19472a3215fe529f5ce7efa54bc","tid":462784,"uid":36035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:02:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc7cf3875068c4e6774f356fa71663bd49f5df33","tid":462784,"uid":36035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"081fae8f79b279d917fd67348f490a5fffd13893","tid":462784,"uid":83568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>縱火咁撚癲<br />\n好似好大獲</blockquote><br />\n縱火判好重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n縱火個性質其實同意圖謀殺差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放火走唔設 一死就死幾件"},{"pid":"81b3c1b13b07bd2a886369aba20c9c22e934ac5c","tid":462784,"uid":4811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"13歲會唔會機已屈？<br />\n希望起碼廿碌，放火真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"c98691c49ee81bc207539d776d1cd9c86b206f6c","tid":462784,"uid":54486,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"cit